xwikidoc.content:
{{velocity}}
$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.description')
#set ($colorThemeDoc = $xwiki.getDocument($xwiki.getXWikiPreference('colorTheme')))

{{warning}}(!) If there are multiple panels in a wiki page, only one style will be applied on all of them, the style of the last defined panel.{{/warning}}

== Parameters ==
The default color values are the values set in the enabled color theme -> [[$colorThemeDoc]]

|=Name|=Description|=Default
|title|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.title.description')|none
|titleColor|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.titleColor.description')|@panel-default-text: $colorThemeDoc.getValue('panel-default-text')
|titleBGColor|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.titleBGColor.description')|@panel-bg: $colorThemeDoc.getValue('panel-bg')
|bgColor|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.bgColor.description')|@panel-bg: $colorThemeDoc.getValue('panel-bg')
|borderStyle|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.borderStyle.description')|solid
|borderColor|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.borderColor.description')|@panel-bg: $colorThemeDoc.getValue('panel-bg')
|borderWidth|$services.localization.render('rendering.macro.panel.parameter.borderWidth.description')|0

